title: Night Flight from Moscow - (El.Serpiente.1973.Yul.Brynner,Henry.
description:
You will watch this again even when you know the ending. Great movie. Lots of intrigue.  Hard to get enough of Yul Brynner. Henry Fonda is always great in any thing he does.

Wide screen, color, english and spanish, dvdrip, no subs, very good quality, just a little off if you watch it on a big screen.


IMDB:
A Russian diplomat hatches a complicated plan to enable him to defect to the West
